description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene ("Bacillus fusiformis" Veillon and Zuber 1898; Corynebacterium fusiforme; Fusibacterium nucleatum; Fusiformis fusiformis; Fusiformis nucleatus; Fusobacterium fusiforme; Fusobacterium plauti-vincenti.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
